org.osframework.spring.chronicle

Class AbstractChronicleBuilderBean.AbstractBuilderConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.osframework.spring.chronicle.AbstractChronicleBuilderBean.AbstractBuilderConfig
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ChronicleMapBuilderBean.ChronicleMapBuilderConfig, ChronicleSetBuilderBean.ChronicleSetBuilderConfig
    Enclosing class:
    AbstractChronicleBuilderBean<K,T>

    protected class AbstractChronicleBuilderBean.AbstractBuilderConfig
extends Object
    Abstract superclass of builder configuration types, used internally by concrete subclasses of AbstractChronicleBuilderBean. Classes which extend this class gain all fields here, as well as provide any specific configuration settings necessary for their associated Chronicle collection type.
